QuestData.Title: Clamming Up
QuestData.Description: Here to help with the clam diving?$B$BGet to it then. There are clams about everywhere just waiting to be dived.
QuestData.CompletionText: Has your clam-laden frolic proved fruitful?
QuestData.RewardText: Well done, indeed. This is an entirely unshameful amount of clams to have gathered. The survivors back at the cave will surely be grateful.
